simulator

Class PathFull

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulator.Path
      • simulator.PathFull
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PathFullInfo

    public class PathFull
extends Path
implements PathFullInfo
    Stores and manipulates a path though a model. The full path is stored, i.e. all info at all steps. State objects and arrays are copied for storage.
